==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ψεύδομαι / pseudomai / psyoo'-dom-ahee
*Middle voice of an apparently primary verb; to utter an untruth or attempt to deceive by falsehood: 

===Verb===
'''ψεύδομαι'''

# falsely, [[lie]].

